---
title: Roast Vegetable, Bulgur Wheat & Chicken Salad with Yoghurt Tahini Dressing
description: There are some vegetables that are made for roasting, and cauliflower is one of them. Golden and caramelised, it works perfectly with chicken and the earthy flavours of tahini dressing and Za'atar spice.
